wood (TV series)|Deadwood]]''\n* [[Balthazar Getty]] \u2013 ''[[Traffic (2004 miniseries)|Traffic]]''\n* [[William H. Macy]] \u2013 ''[[Stealing Sinatra]]''\n* [[Keith McErlean]] \u2013 ''[[The Blackwater Lightship (film)|The Blackwater Lightship]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | 2005\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | '''[[Randy Quaid]] \u2013 ''[[Elvis (miniseries)|Elvis]]'''''\n|\n* [[Brian Dennehy]] \u2013 ''[[Our Fathers (film)|Our Fathers]]''\n* [[Tim Blake Nelson]] \u2013 ''[[Warm Springs (film)|Warm Springs]]''\n* [[Paul Newman]] \u2013 ''[[Empire Falls (miniseries)|Empire Falls]]''\n* [[Ruben Santiago-Hudson]] \u2013 ''[[Their Eyes Were Watching God (film)|Their Eyes Were Watching God]]''\n* [[William Shatner]] \u2013 ''[[Boston Legal]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | 2006\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | '''[[Tony Plana]] \u2013 ''[[Ugly Betty]]'''''\n|\n* [[Philip Baker Hall]] \u2013 ''[[The Loop (U.S. TV series)|The Loop]]''\n* [[Michael Emerson]] \u2013 ''[[Lost (TV series)|Lost]]''\n* [[Robert Knepper]] \u2013 ''[[Prison Break]]''\n* [[Jeremy Piven]] \u2013 ''[[Entourage (U.S. TV series)|Entourage]]''\n* [[Forest Whitaker]] \u2013 ''[[The Shield]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | 2007\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | '''[[David Zayas]] \u2013 ''[[Dexter (TV series)|Dexter]]'''''\n|\n* [[Harry Dean Stanton]] \u2013 ''[[Big Love]]''\n* [[Michael Emerson]] \u2013 ''[[Lost (TV series)|Lost]]''\n* [[Justin Kirk]] \u2013 ''[[Weeds (TV series)|Weeds]]''\n* [[T. R. Knight]] \u2013 ''[[Grey's Anatomy]]''\n* [[Masi Oka]] \u2013 ''[[Heroes (U.S. TV series)|Heroes]]''\n* [[Andy Serkis]] \u2013 ''[[Longford (film)|Longford]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | 2008\n| align=\"center\" valign=\"center\"; | '''[[Nelsan Ellis]] \u2013 ''[[True Blood]]'''''\n|\n* [[\u017deljko Ivanek]] \u2013 ''[[Damages (TV series)|Damages]]''\n* [[Harvey Keitel]] \u2013 ''[[Life on Mars (U.S. TV series)|Life